{"tid":306151,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企搬屋有好多二手野想賣","createTime":"2017-07-02T09:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T18:05:33.000Z","uid":69159,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"073e0b2e0d96df899f5e086b4abdc314ebd4f901","tid":306151,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"最近搬屋,屋企有D手機零件、音響、電腦、CD等<br />\n好多野想賣出去俾人<br />\n唔想咁浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無咩APP或者網頁可以做到呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n平時無咩接觸呢D平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好可以近D交易,唔想周圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8df0535747934be9ea13dee38853a4427bd8f94","tid":306151,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:45:37.000Z","msg":"我都係，過兩個月搬屋企有好多野都唔會帶去。"},{"pid":"d919fbc05072c482ebd40ecf76c55006d966a069","tid":306151,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係，過兩個月搬屋企有好多野都唔會帶去。</blockquote><br />\n會唔會想賣？"},{"pid":"159c110928777adc66b9aa1f8967516ba4da8333","tid":306151,"uid":5499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:13:26.000Z","msg":"你都係想係到賣姐"},{"pid":"906fccacfc04738a3ae2532535e93322df7dac05","tid":306151,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"打比收買佬"},{"pid":"80e630e48c12ec28e93d2cdaa40dd3a4c418f5a8","tid":306151,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係，過兩個月搬屋企有好多野都唔會帶去。</blockquote><br />\n會唔會想賣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇啊，最多唔要既係 dvd 書舊衫舊遊戲機，如果唔搞到時分分鐘掉哂佢，咁掉又好似好浪費，其它雪櫃微波爐衣櫃書架梳化電腦枱好多野都唔會搬過去。"},{"pid":"2b54cdd8903520d47e9e11287324c33aab7184ba","tid":306151,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:30:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打比收買佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家搵緊 d 慈善